307
00:22:38,930 --> 00:22:42,600
Oh... I'll drop by her store.

308
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:44,080
Okay.

309
00:22:50,650 --> 00:22:52,390
Please excuse me.

310
00:22:54,450 --> 00:22:55,810
Have you heard?

311
00:22:55,810 --> 00:22:57,680
