362
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:11,580
And I have a kid, so I wonder if I can still find love.

363
00:26:11,580 --> 00:26:15,460
- Well, about that-
- But I got divorced because my ex cheated on me.

364
00:26:15,460 --> 00:26:18,210
